\lim \limits_{(x,y) \to (x_0, 1)}\frac{x}{y^2-1}
\lim \limits_{(x,y) \to (x_0, 1)}\left(\dfrac{x}{y^2-1}\right)\in \mathbb R
\lim \limits_{(x,y) \to (x_0, 1)}\left(\dfrac{x}{y+1}\right)\in \mathbb R
\lim \limits_{(x,y) \to (x_0, 1)}\left(\dfrac{1}{y-1}\right)\in \mathbb R
\lim \limits_{y\to 1}\left(\dfrac{1}{1-y}\right)
